#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:56 index.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Sissejuhatus"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is &gwenview;"
msgstr "Mis on &gwenview;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "&gwenview; is a fast and easy to use image and video viewer."
msgstr "&gwenview; on kiire ja lihtne piltide ja videode näitamise rakendus."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gwenview; features two main modes: Browse and View. Both modes can be used "
"in a normal application window and Full Screen. Browse Mode lets you "
"navigate through your computer showing thumbnails of your images, View Mode "
"lets you view images one at a time, and Full Screen lets you make quick "
"slideshows. There is also a start screen that displays a list of recently "
"opened folders and &URL;s as well as your places and tags."
msgstr ""
"&gwenview; võib töötada kahes režiimis: sirvimine ja näitamine. Mõlemat saab "
"kasutada nii tavalises rakenduseaknas kui ka täisekraanirežiimis. "
"Sirvimisrežiim võimaldab vabalt liikuda failisüsteemis, näidates pisipilte, "
"näitamisrežiim võimaldab vaadata korraga üht pilti ning täisekraanirežiim "
"lubab luua lausa slaidiseansse. On olemas ka avaaken, mis näitab nii viimati "
"avatud kaustu ja &URL;-e kui ka sinu asukohti ja silte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Image loading is handled by the &Qt; library, so &gwenview; supports all "
"image formats your &Qt; installation supports. &gwenview; correctly displays "
"images with an alpha channel (transparency) as well as animations."
msgstr ""
"Piltide avamisega tegeleb &Qt; teek, mistõttu &gwenview; toetab kõiki neid "
"pildivorminguid, mida toetab ka &Qt;. &gwenview; suudab korrektselt näidata "
"nii alfakanaliga (läbipaistvaid) pilte kui ka animatsioone."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gwenview; supports the displaying and editing of EXIF comments in JPEG "
"images. Lossless JPEG transforms such as rotations and mirroring are also "
"supported."
msgstr ""
"&gwenview; toetab ka EXIF-kommentaaride näitamist ja muutmist, kui "
"paigaldatud on vastav JPEG plugin. Seda pakub KDE moodul kdegraphics. "
"Toetatud on JPEG kadudeta teisendus, näiteks pööramine ja peegeldamine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gwenview; can read embedded color profiles from PNG and JPEG files. It can "
"use the image color profile together with the display color profile to "
"output correct colors on the screen."
msgstr ""
"&gwenview; suudab lugeda PNG- ja JPEG-failidesse põimitud värviprofiile. "
"Ühtlasi saab pildi värviprofiili koos kuvari värviprofiiliga kasutada "
"väljundvärvide korrigeerimiseks ekraanil."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Interface"
msgstr "Kasutajaliides"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start Page"
msgstr "Avalehekülg"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The start page lists recently opened folders and &URL;s on the left side, "
"and your places and tags on the right side."
msgstr ""
"Avalehekülg näitab vasakul viimati avatud katalooge ja &URL;-e ning paremal "
"sinu asukohti ja silte."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start Page Screenshot"
msgstr "Avalehekülje pilt"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Image Operations"
msgstr "Pilditoimingud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gwenview; has a few features which are available in both Browse, View, and "
"Full Screen view. &gwenview; has the capability to do basic alteration of "
"your images."
msgstr ""
"&gwenview; mõned omadused on saadaval nii sirvimis-, näitamis- kui ka "
"täisekraanirežiimis. &gwenview; suudab teatud määral ka pilte muuta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Rotate: A rotate operation will rotate the image either to the left or to "
#| "the right, depending on whether you do <menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo "
#| "action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
#| "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rotate Right</guimenuitem> </"
#| "menuchoice> or <menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
#| "<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
#| "<guimenuitem>Rotate Left</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgid ""
"Rotate: A rotate operation will rotate the image either to the left or to "
"the right, depending on whether you do <menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rotate Right</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> or <menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Shift;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Rotate Left</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Pööramine: pööramistoiminguga saab pilti pöörata kas vasakule või paremale "
"sõltuvalt sellest, kas valida <menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pööra paremale</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> või <menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pööra vasakule</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mirror</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>: This operation will reflect the image along the vertical axis, "
"as if you were seeing it in a mirror."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Peegelda</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: võimaldab peegeldada pilti piki püsttelge, nagu "
"näeks seda peeglis."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Flip</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>: This operation will reflect the image upside-down (a reflection "
"along the horizontal axis)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pööra pea peale</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: võimaldab peegeldada pilti piki rõhttelge ehk "
"keerata tagurpidi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>R</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Resize</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: This operation will allow you to shrink or "
"expand the image. Note that if you increase the size of an image, it may "
"appear blurry and/or pixelated."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>R</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Muuda suurust</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: võimaldab pilti "
"suurendada või vähendada. Pane tähele, et kui suurendad pilti, võib see "
"muutuda hägusaks ja/või kattuda ruudukestega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These actions are also available on the <guilabel>Operations</guilabel> tab "
"of the sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Need toimingud on saadaval ka külgriba kaardil <guilabel>Toimingud</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have edited one or more images a bar with additional actions is "
"displayed at the top of the image. You can undo or redo your changes, go to "
"the previous or next modified image and there are three options to save the "
"changed images."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled muutnud vähemalt üht pilti, ilmub pildi kohale riba "
"lisatoimingutega. Muudatusi saab tühistada või uuesti teha, võib liikuda "
"eelmisele või järgmisele muudetud pildile ning muudetud pildi salvestamiseks "
"on lausa kolm võimalust."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Actions bar for modified images"
msgstr "Muudetud piltide toiminguriba"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browse Mode"
msgstr "Sirvimisrežiim"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When in Browse Mode, you can easily navigate through your files and folders. "
"The preview window shows thumbnails of the images in the current folder, as "
"well as subfolders."
msgstr ""
"Sirvimisrežiimis saab hõlpsasti liikuda oma failide ja kataloogide vahel. "
"Eelvaatluse aknas saab näha nii aktiivse kataloogi kui ka selle "
"alamkataloogide pisipilte."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browse Mode Screenshot"
msgstr "Sirvimisrežiim"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Moving the mouse over an image shows buttons to select or rotate the image "
"as well as a button to enter Fullscreen Mode. Modified images are indicated "
"by an icon down right, click it to save the changed image. Clicking on an "
"image takes you into View Mode. You may select multiple images and switch to "
"View Mode to view them side-by-side."
msgstr ""
"Hiire liigutamisel pildi kohale näeb nuppe, millega saab pilti valida või "
"keerata, samuti minna täisekraanirežiimi. Muudetud pilte tunneb ära ikooni "
"järgi all paremal, millele klõpsates saab muudetud pildi salvestada. Pildil "
"klõpsamine viib vaaterežiimi. Valida võib mitu ka mitu pilti ja lülituda "
"siis vaaterežiimi, kus neid näeb kõrvuti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The slider at the bottom right allows you to change the size of the images. "
"You can also filter the images by filename, date, tag or rating using the "
"box on the lower left. The toolbar appears in both Browse mode as well as "
"View mode and contains the most commonly used actions."
msgstr ""
"Liugur all paremal võimaldab muuta piltide suurust. All vasakul asuva kasti "
"abil saab pilte filtreerida failinime, kuupäeva, sildi või hinnangu järgi. "
"Tööriistariba on näha nii sirvimis- kui ka vaaterežiimis ning sisaldab kõige "
"levinumate toimingute ikoone."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guiicon>Start Page</guiicon>: Open the start page."
msgstr "<guiicon>Avalehekülg</guiicon>: avalehekülje avamine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guiicon>Browse</guiicon>: Switches to Browse Mode."
msgstr "<guiicon>Sirvimine</guiicon>: lülitumine sirvimisrežiimi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guiicon>View</guiicon>: Switches to View Mode."
msgstr "<guiicon>Vaade</guiicon>: lülitumine näitamisrežiimi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon>Previous</guiicon>: Clicking this icon will go to the previous "
"image in the folder."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon>Eelmine</guiicon>: sellele ikoonile klõpsates liigutakse kataloogi "
"eelmisele pildile."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon>Next</guiicon>: Clicking this button will go to the next image in "
"the folder."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon>Järgmine</guiicon>: sellele nupule klõpsates liigutakse kataloogi "
"järgmisele pildile."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon>Show Editing Tools</guiicon>: Clicking this button toggles the "
"<link linkend=\"sidebar\">Operations sidebar tab</link>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guiicon>Full Screen</guiicon>: Switches to Full Screen Mode."
msgstr "<guiicon>Täisekraan</guiicon>: lülitumine täisekraanirežiimi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Mode"
msgstr "Näitamisrežiim"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "View Mode displays full-size images. The same <link linkend=\"sidebar"
#| "\">sidebar</link> available in Browse Mode is displayed on the left. At "
#| "the bottom, there is the Thumbnail Bar, which allows you to scroll "
#| "through the images in the current folder. The Thumbnail Bar can be "
#| "minimized by clicking on the <guibutton>Thumbnail Bar</guibutton> button. "
#| "Clicking again will restore it. To change the size of the thumbnails move "
#| "the splitter with the &LMB;."
msgid ""
"View Mode displays full-size images. The same <link linkend=\"sidebar"
"\">sidebar</link> available in Browse Mode is displayed on the left. At the "
"bottom, there is the Thumbnail Bar, which allows you to scroll through the "
"images in the current folder. The Thumbnail Bar can be unfolded by clicking "
"on the <guibutton>Show Thumbnails</guibutton> button. Clicking again will "
"fold it. To change the size of the thumbnails move the splitter with the "
"&LMB;."
msgstr ""
"Vaaterežiimis näidatakse täissuuruses pilte. Vasakul asub samasugune <link "
"linkend=\"sidebar\">külgriba</link> nagu sirvimisrežiimis. All asub "
"pisipildiriba, mis võimaldab kerida läbi aktiivse kataloogi piltide. "
"Pisipildiriba saab minimeerida, kui klõpsata <guibutton>pisipildiriba</"
"guibutton> nupul. Nupul uuesti klõpsates riba taastatakse. Pisipiltide "
"suuruse muutmiseks liiguta eraldajat &HVNga;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"View Mode supports viewing multiple images side-by-side. You may select "
"multiple images in Browse Mode before switching to View Mode, or you may "
"click the <guibutton>+</guibutton> button that appears when hovering over "
"images in the Thumbnail Bar to add a pane displaying that image. A "
"<guibutton>-</guibutton> will then appear that will permit you to remove its "
"pane."
msgstr ""
"Vaaterežiim toetab mitme pildi näitamist üksteise kõrval. Mitu pilti võib "
"valida sirvimisrežiimis enne vaaterežiimile lülitumist või siis nupuga "
"<guibutton>+</guibutton>, mis ilmub, kui viia hiir pisipildiribal pildi "
"kohale, ja võimaldab lisada seda pilti näitava paneeli. Seejärel ilmub ka "
"nupp <guibutton>-</guibutton>, mis võimaldab paneeli eemaldada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When multiple images are displayed, a small toolbar appears below each image "
"that permits you to delete the image or remove its pane. You may perform "
"zoom operations independently for each image, or synchronize them. Toggle "
"this by checking the <guilabel>Synchronize</guilabel> to the left of the "
"zoom slider or by pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Y</"
"keycap></keycombo>. You can switch images by clicking on their pane, or "
"using your keyboard. To switch to the image on the right, press <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Tab;</keycombo>. To switch to the image on the left, press "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&Tab;</keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Mitme pildi näitamisel ilmub iga pildi alla väike tööriistariba, mis lubab "
"pildi kustutada või eemaldada selle paneeli. Iga pilti võib eraldi "
"suurendada ja vähendada, aga seda võib teha ka sünkroonselt. Seda saab "
"määrata suurendusliugurist vasakul asuva märkekastiga "
"<guilabel>Sünkroniseerimine</guilabel> või vajutades kiirklahvi <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Y</keycap></keycombo>. Piltide vahel saab "
"lülituda nende paneelile klõpsates või klaviatuuri abil. Parempoolsele "
"pildile lülitumiseks vajuta klahvi <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Tab;</"
"keycombo>. Vasakpoolsele pildile lülitumiseks vajuta klahve <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Shift;&Tab;</keycombo>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Mode Screenshot"
msgstr "Näitamisrežiim"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:254
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The slider at the bottom right controls the zoom of the image. The "
#| "<guibutton>Fit</guibutton> button and the <guibutton>100%</guibutton> "
#| "button are next to the zoom slider and are two preset zoom levels. The "
#| "<guibutton>Fit</guibutton> button zooms the current image to fit the size "
#| "of the window, and the <guibutton>100%</guibutton> button zooms the image "
#| "to the actual pixel size. The shortcut <keycap>F</keycap> toggles between "
#| "both view modes."
msgid ""
"The slider at the bottom right controls the zoom of the image. The "
"<guibutton>Fit</guibutton>, <guibutton>Fill</guibutton> and <guibutton>100%</"
"guibutton> buttons are next to the zoom slider and are three preset zoom "
"levels. The <guibutton>Fit</guibutton> button zooms the current image to fit "
"the size of the window, the <guibutton>Fill</guibutton> button zooms the "
"image to fill the window by fitting width or height and the <guibutton>100%</"
"guibutton> button zooms the image to the actual pixel size. The shortcut "
"<keycap>F</keycap> toggles between <guibutton>Fit</guibutton> mode and "
"<guibutton>100%</guibutton>, pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;"
"<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> will toggle <guibutton>Fill</guibutton> "
"respectively."
msgstr ""
"All paremal asuva liuguriga saab muuta pildi suurendus. Nupud "
"<guibutton>Mahuta</guibutton> ja <guibutton>100%</guibutton> asuvad otse "
"suurendusliuguri kõrval ning neile klõpsates saab valida eelnevalt määratud "
"suurendustaseme, mis vastab mainitud nuppude nimetusele. Nupp "
"<guibutton>Mahuta</guibutton> suurendab või vähendab pilti, et see mahuks "
"kenasti aknasse, nupp <guibutton>100%</guibutton> näitab pilti just nii "
"suurena, nagu see tegelikult on. Vaaterežiimide vahel saab lülituda "
"kiirklahviga <keycap>F</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When an image is in zoom-to-fit mode, you can go to the previous and next "
"image with the arrow keys. When you zoom in, arrow keys are used to scroll "
"the image. This is very similar to the behavior provided by phones or "
"digital cameras."
msgstr ""
"Kui pilt on suurendatud aknasse sobivaks, saab eelmisele ja järgmisele "
"pildile liikuda nooleklahvidega. Kui pilti suurendad, saab nooleklahvidega "
"seda kerida. See käitumine sarnaneb sellele, mida võib kohata telefonides "
"või digitaalkaamerates."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:266
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When an image is zoomed in, a bird-eye view appears and lets you scroll "
#| "the image using the mouse and the arrow keys. The bird-eye view "
#| "automatically hides itself after a short delay, showing back only while "
#| "zooming or scrolling."
msgid ""
"When an image is zoomed in, a bird's eye view appears and lets you scroll "
"the image using the mouse and the arrow keys. The bird's eye view "
"automatically hides itself after a short delay, showing back only while "
"zooming or scrolling. The bird's eye view can be disabled from the right "
"click context menu or from <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Bird's Eye View When Zoomed In</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Kui pilt on suurendatud, ilmub ülevaade, mis võimaldab pilti kerida nii "
"nooleklahvide kui ka hiirega. Ülevaade kaob automaatselt lühikese viivituse "
"järel ning ilmub taas nähtavale ainult siis, kui taas suurendad või vähendad "
"või pilti kerid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can define what happens when going to image B after having zoomed in on "
"an area of image A using the options in the <guilabel>Zoom mode</guilabel> "
"group on the <guimenuitem>Image View</guimenuitem> page of the &gwenview; "
"configuration window which can be reached using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &gwenview;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Saab määrata, mis juhtub siis, kui liigud pildile B pärast seda, kui oled "
"pildil A mõnda piirkonda suurendanud, kasutades valikuid lehekülje "
"<guimenuitem>Pildivaade</guimenuitem> sektsioonis <guilabel>Suurendusrežiim</"
"guilabel> &gwenview; seadistustedialoogis, mille saab avada menüükäsuga "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu><guimenuitem>&gwenview; "
"seadistamine...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If set to <guilabel>Autofit each image</guilabel>, image B is zoomed out to "
"fit the screen."
msgstr ""
"Kui valida <guilabel>Kõigi piltide automaatne sobitamine</guilabel>, "
"vähendatakse pilti B ekraanile mahutamiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If set to <guilabel>Keep same zoom and position</guilabel>, all images share "
"the same zoom and position: image B is set to the same zoom parameters as "
"image A (and if these are changed, image A will then be displayed with the "
"updated zoom and position)."
msgstr ""
"Kui valida <guilabel>Sama suurenduse ja asukoha säilitamine</guilabel>, on "
"kõigil piltidel sama suurendus ja asukoht: pildile B määratakse samad "
"suurendusparameetrid nagu pildile A (ja kui need muutuvad, siis kuvatakse "
"pilti A samuti uuendatud suurenduse ja asukohaga)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If set to <guilabel>Per image zoom and position</guilabel>, all images "
"remember their own zoom and position: image B is initially set to the same "
"zoom parameters as image A, but will then remember its own zoom and position "
"(if these are changed, image A will <emphasis>not</emphasis> be displayed "
"with the updated zoom and position)."
msgstr ""
"Kui valida <guilabel>Pildikaupa suurendus ja asukoht</guilabel>, jätavad "
"kõik pildid meelde oma suurenduse ja asukoha: pildile B määratakse algul "
"samad suurendusparameetrid nagu pildile B, aga seejärel jätab ta meelde "
"omaenda suurenduse ja asukoha (kui neid muudetakse, siis pilti A "
"<emphasis>ei kuvata</emphasis> uuendatud suurenduse ja asukohaga)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can start directly in View mode by starting &gwenview; from a context "
"menu like <guimenuitem>Open With</guimenuitem> in another program or by "
"launching it from the command line with an image as an argument."
msgstr ""
"Näitamisrežiimi saab ka otse käivitada, kui käivitada &gwenview; "
"kontekstimenüüst, näiteks mõne teise rakenduse käsuga <guimenuitem>Ava "
"rakendusega</guimenuitem>, või käsurealt, kui anda argumendina avatav pilt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following additional image operations are available only in View Mode:"
msgstr "Järgmisi täiendavaid pilditoiminguid saab teha ainult vaaterežiimis:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>C</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Crop</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: This operation lets you discard parts of the "
"image you don't want."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>C</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Kärbi</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: võimaldab kõrvaldada pildi "
"osad, mida sa ei soovi näha."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can access the advanced cropping parameters by ticking "
"<guilabel>Advanced settings</guilabel> check box on the bottom popup pane. "
"Use the corresponding fields to tune up the cropping operation."
msgstr ""
"Täiendavaid kärpimisvalikuid saab kasutada, kui märkida all hüpikpaneelil "
"kastike <guilabel>Muud seadistused</guilabel>. Vastavate väljadega saab "
"kärpimist täppishäälestada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is also possible to adjust the cropped area by dragging the gray square "
"handles on the borders of the image. You can move the cropped area by "
"clicking and holding the &LMB; and drag it with the mouse pointer."
msgstr ""
"Kärbitavat ala saab samuti kohandada pildi ääristel olevaid halle "
"ruudukujulisi pidemeid lohistades. Kärbitavat ala saab liigutada, kui "
"klõpsata sellel &HVNga; ja nuppu all hoides ala lohistada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>Crop</guibutton> button to see the results when you are "
"ready. Use the upper popup pane to save the results or undo/redo the "
"operation."
msgstr ""
"Klõpsuga nupule <guibutton>Kärbi</guibutton> saab näha tulemust. Ülemise "
"hüpikpaneeli abil saab toimingut tühistada või uuesti teha ning tulemust "
"salvestada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:306
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Red Eye Reduction</"
#| "guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: This operation reduces the \"red eye\" effect "
#| "commonly found in photographs taken with a flash camera."
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reduce Red Eye</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: This operation reduces the \"red eye\" effect "
"commonly found in photographs taken with a flash camera."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Punasilmsuse "
"vähendamine</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: võimaldab vähendada nõndanimetatud "
"punasilmsust, mida leidub sageli välklambiga tehtud fotodel."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid "Full Screen Modes"
msgstr "Täisekraanirežiimid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Access Full Screen by pressing the <guiicon>Full Screen</guiicon> button on "
"the toolbar, or by <menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Full Screen Mode</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Täisekraanirežiimi saab minna, kui klõpsata tööriistaribal nuppu "
"<guiicon>Täisekraan</guiicon> või valida menüükäsk <menuchoice> <shortcut> "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Täisekraanirežiim</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid "To leave this mode press the &Esc; key."
msgstr "Režiimist väljumiseks vajuta klahvi &Esc;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browse Mode Full Screen"
msgstr "Sirvimisrežiimi täisekraan"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In Browse Mode you can switch to fullscreen also by clicking on the button "
"that appears when you move the mouse over the thumbnails."
msgstr ""
"Sirvimisrežiimis saab minna täisekraanirežiimi ka nupule klõpsates, mis "
"ilmub nähtavale, kui liigutad hiirt pisipiltide kohal."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Full Screen View Mode Screenshot"
msgstr "Näitamisrežiimi täisekraani pilt"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Going fullscreen while browsing gives you a more immersive experience while "
"you go through your pictures. It is quite nice on your regular computer, but "
"makes even more sense when you connect your laptop to the big TV in the "
"living room to show pictures to your guests."
msgstr ""
"Täisekraan sirvimise ajal tagab piltide vahel liikudes palju võimsama "
"elamuse. See on tore juba tavalisel arvutiekraanil, aga veel enam siis, kui "
"ühendad oma sülearvuti elutoa suure teleekraaniga ja näitad pilte külla "
"tulnud sõpradele."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Mode Full Screen"
msgstr "Näitamisrežiimi täisekraan"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The full screen View Mode shows a slideshow of your images. Access Full "
"Screen Mode by clicking on the button that appears when you move the mouse "
"over the thumbnails in Browse Mode, by pressing the <guiicon>Full Screen</"
"guiicon> button on the taskbar."
msgstr ""
"Täisekraanirežiimis saab vaadata oma piltide slaidiseanssi. "
"Täisekraanirežiimi avamiseks klõpsa nupule, mis ilmub sirvimisrežiimis "
"hiirega pisipildi kohale liikudes, klõpsates tegumiribal nupule "
"<guiicon>Täisekraan</guiicon>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Full Screen Browse Mode Screenshot"
msgstr "Sirvimisrežiimi täisekraani pilt"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:371
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The top bar will hide itself automatically; to show it simply move the "
#| "mouse to the top of the screen. If the mouse cursor is over the top bar, "
#| "it will not autohide. Most of the buttons on the bar are the same as the "
#| "ones on the toolbar in Browse or View Modes, except for the <guiicon>Exit "
#| "Full Screen Mode</guiicon> button which returns you to the &gwenview; "
#| "window, the <guiicon>Start/Stop Slideshow</guiicon> button, and the "
#| "<guiicon>Configure Full Screen Mode</guiicon> button which shows a small "
#| "settings dialog that allows you to easily and quickly configure the "
#| "slideshow. The slideshow controls there are:"
msgid ""
"The top bar will hide itself automatically; to show it simply move the mouse "
"to the top of the screen. If the mouse cursor is over the top bar, it will "
"not autohide. Most of the buttons on the bar are the same as the ones on the "
"toolbar in Browse or View Modes, except for the <guiicon>Exit Full Screen "
"Mode</guiicon> button which returns you to the &gwenview; window, the "
"<guiicon>Pause/Resume Slideshow</guiicon> button, and the <guiicon>Configure "
"Full Screen Mode</guiicon> button which shows a small settings dialog that "
"allows you to easily and quickly configure the slideshow. The slideshow "
"controls there are:"
msgstr ""
"Ülariba peitub automaatselt, aga kui soovid seda näha, viis lihtsalt hiir "
"ekraani ülaossa. Kui hiirekursor asub ülariba kohal, ei lähe see peitu. "
"Enamik riba nuppe on samad, mis sirvimis- või näitamisrežiimi "
"tööriistaribal, välja arvatud <guiicon>Välju täisekraanirežiimist</guiicon>, "
"mis viib tagasi &gwenview; aknasse, <guiicon>Käivita/Peata slaidiseanss</"
"guiicon> ning <guiicon>Seadista täisekraanirežiimi</guiicon>, mis avab "
"väikese seadistustedialoogi, kus saab kiiresti seadistada slaidiseanssi. "
"Dialoogi valikud on järgmised:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Interval</guilabel> slider controls how long &gwenview; will "
"show an image before it move to the next one."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Intervall</guilabel>iliuguriga saab määrata, kui kaua näitab "
"&gwenview; pilti, enne kui liigub järgmise juurde."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Loop</guilabel> check box is checked, when the end of the "
"slideshow is reached, it will continue from the beginning instead of "
"stopping."
msgstr ""
"Kui märgitud on kastike <guilabel>Kordus</guilabel>, siis jätkatakse "
"slaidiseansi lõppu jõudes seda uuesti algusest, mitte ei peatuta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Random</guilabel> check box is checked, instead of "
"progressing through the folder alphabetically, images will be shown in "
"random order."
msgstr ""
"Kui märgitud on kastike <guilabel>Juhuslik</guilabel>, siis ei liiguta läbi "
"kataloogi mitte tähestikuliselt, vaid näidatakse pilte juhuslikus "
"järjekorras."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Select Image Information to Display</guibutton> allows you to "
"define what metadata is displayed under the buttons on the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Vali näidatav pilditeave</guibutton> võimaldab määrata, milliseid "
"metaandmeid kuvatakse tööriistariba nuppude all."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Show thumbnails</guilabel> check box is checked, thumbnails "
"for all images in the current folder will be displayed to the right of the "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Kui märgitud on kastike <guilabel>Pisipiltide näitamine</guilabel>, siis "
"näidatakse tööriistaribast paremal kõigi aktiivse kataloogi piltide "
"pisipilte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Height</guilabel> slider changes the size of the thumbnails "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Kõrgus</guilabel>eliugur võimaldab muuta kuvatavate pisipiltide "
"suurust."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, an area that shows you the other images in the current folder "
"will be shown on the top bar. Clicking on one will display it."
msgstr ""
"Märkimise korral näidatakse ülaribal piirkonda, mis näitab aktiivse "
"kataloogi teisi pilte. Mõnel neist klõpsates näidatakse vastavat pilti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sidebar"
msgstr "Külgriba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sidebar on the left is available in the Browse and View modes, but does "
"not appear by default in Browse Mode. Its appearance can be toggled using "
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycap>F4</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sidebar</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or using the "
"<guiicon>▮←</guiicon> / <guiicon>▮→</guiicon> button at the left side of the "
"statusbar. When clicked it collapses or expands the sidebar. The sidebar "
"contains several tabs:"
msgstr ""
"Vasakul asuvat külgriba saab näha sirvimis- ja vaaterežiimis, kuid esimeses "
"seda vaikimisi ei näidata. Selle saab avada <menuchoice> <shortcut> "
"<keycap>F4</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Külgriba</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> või nupuga <guiicon>▮←</"
"guiicon> / <guiicon>▮→</guiicon> olekuriba vasakus servas. Viimasele "
"klõpsates külgriba keritakse vastavalt kokku või lahti. Külgriba sisaldab "
"mitut kaarti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folders"
msgstr "Kataloogid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:425
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Displays a list of all folders on your system permitting you to switch "
#| "between them. In Browse Mode thumbnails from the folder will be "
#| "displayed, while in View Mode the first image in the folder will appear, "
#| "from which you can browse through the folder using the "
#| "<guibutton>Previous</guibutton> and <guibutton>Next</guibutton> buttons "
#| "or shortcuts."
msgid ""
"Displays a list of all folders on your system permitting you to switch "
"between them. In Browse Mode thumbnails from the folder will be displayed, "
"while in View Mode the first image in the folder will appear, from which you "
"can browse through the folder using the <guibutton>Previous</guibutton> and "
"<guibutton>Next</guibutton> buttons or shortcuts. Clicking on a folder "
"multiple times toggles between View Mode and Browse Mode."
msgstr ""
"Näitab sinu süsteemi kõigi kataloogide nimekirja, mis võimaldab nende vahel "
"liikuda. Sirvimisrežiimis näidatakse kataloogide pisipilte, vaaterežiimis "
"aga kataloogi esimest pilti, mis lubab kataloogi läbi sirvida nuppudega "
"<guibutton>Eelmine</guibutton> ja <guibutton>Järgmine</guibutton> või "
"kiirklahvidega."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid "Information"
msgstr "Teave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays <guilabel>Meta Information</guilabel> like the filename and size. "
"The <guilabel>More...</guilabel> link permits you to view all available "
"metadata and select which data appear in the sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Näitab <guilabel>metainfot</guilabel>, näiteks failinime ja suurust. Link "
"<guilabel>Rohkem...</guilabel> lubab näha kõiki saadaolevaid metaandmeid ja "
"valida, millised neist on näha külgribal."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid "Operations"
msgstr "Toimingud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This permits you to perform the <link linkend=\"image_operations"
"\">previously described global image operations</link> as well as those "
"specific to View Mode. It also permits common file operations like copying, "
"renaming, deleting, and creating new folders."
msgstr ""
"Võimaldab sooritada nii <link linkend=\"image_operations\">eelnevalt "
"kirjeldatud globaalseid pilditoiminguid</link> kui ka vaaterežiimi "
"spetsiifilisi toiminguid. Samuti lubab see ette võtta levinumaid "
"failitoiminguid, näiteks kopeerimine, nime muutmine, kustutamine ja uute "
"kataloogide loomine."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:453
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "&kappname; Importer"
msgid "&gwenview; Importer"
msgstr "&kappname; importija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:457
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The &kappname; Importer allows you to import images from a digital camera "
#| "or removable media. To launch it, select <guilabel>Download Photos with "
#| "&kappname;</guilabel> in the &kde; Device Notifier after connecting a "
#| "supported device."
msgid ""
"The &gwenview; Importer allows you to import images from a digital camera or "
"removable media. To launch it, select <guilabel>Download Photos with "
"&gwenview;</guilabel> in the &kde; Device Notifier after connecting a "
"supported device."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; importija võimaldab importida pilte digitaalkaamerast või "
"eemaldatavalt andmekandjalt. Selle käivitamiseks vali pärast toetatud seadme "
"arvutiga ühendamist &kde; seadmete teadustajas <guilabel>Fotode "
"allalaadimine &kappname;'ga</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:461
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you plug in a device the &kappname; importer recursively lists all "
#| "images and videos."
msgid ""
"When you plug in a device the &gwenview; importer recursively lists all "
"images and videos."
msgstr ""
"Seadme ühendamisel tuvastab &kappname; importija rekusriivselt kõik pildid "
"ja videod."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is not always what you expect, &eg; plugging a smartphone you do not "
"want to list all medias of the device; but only the pictures you took, which "
"are usually in a special subfolder."
msgstr ""
"See ei pruugi anda alati soovitud tulemusi: näiteks nutitelefoni ühendamisel "
"ei pruugi olla mõttekas näha kõiki seadme meediafaile, vaid ainult tehtud "
"pilte, mis on tavaliselt spetsiaalses alamkataloogis."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid "Root Folder Picking"
msgstr "Juurkataloogi valimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "It is possible to select the root folder to list, and &kappname; Importer "
#| "will remember the last root folder for each device. This way, next time "
#| "you plug a device in, only the relevant pictures and videos should be "
#| "listed."
msgid ""
"It is possible to select the root folder to list, and &gwenview; Importer "
"will remember the last root folder for each device. This way, next time you "
"plug a device in, only the relevant pictures and videos should be listed."
msgstr ""
"Selleks on võimalik valida juurkataloog, mille sisu näidata. &kappname; "
"importija jätab iga seadme jaoks meelde viimase juurkataloogi. Sel moel "
"näidatakse seadme järgmisel ühendamisel ainult vajalikke pilte ja videoid."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing Images"
msgstr "Piltide importimine"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:484
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "&kappname; Importer Screenshot"
msgid "&gwenview; Importer Screenshot"
msgstr "&kappname; importija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you wish, you may select the images you want to import under "
"<guilabel>Select the documents to import</guilabel> by pressing the <guiicon>"
"+</guiicon> button that appears when hovering over an image. You may also "
"select the folder that images are imported to in the text box at the bottom "
"of the window. When you are done, click the <guibutton>Import Selected</"
"guibutton> button to import only the images you have selected, or click "
"<guibutton>Import All</guibutton> to import all images found on the device."
msgstr ""
"Soovi korral võid dialoogis <guilabel>Imporditavate dokumentide valimine</"
"guilabel> valida pildid, mida soovid importida, vajutades nupule <guiicon>+</"
"guiicon>, mis ilmub hiirekursorit pildi kohale viies. Samuti võib valida "
"kataloogi, mille pildid imporditakse, akna allosas asuvas tekstikastis. Kui "
"oled valmis, klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Impordi valitud</guibutton>, et "
"importida ainult valitud pildid, või <guibutton>Impordi kõik</guibutton>, et "
"importida kõik seadmes leitud pildid."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic Renaming"
msgstr "Automaatne ümbernimetamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:503
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; Importer can rename your files according to a specified "
#| "pattern. To configure this, select the <guibutton>Settings</guibutton> in "
#| "the lower left corner. You may turn this feature on or off using the "
#| "check box at the top. The <guilabel>Rename Format</guilabel> supports "
#| "several special parameters, which will be replaced by metadata such as "
#| "the date the image was created or its filename. They are listed below the "
#| "text box. You may either click on the parameter name to enter it into the "
#| "text box or type one manually."
msgid ""
"&gwenview; Importer can rename your files according to a specified pattern. "
"To configure this, select the <guibutton>Settings</guibutton> in the lower "
"left corner. You may turn this feature on or off using the check box at the "
"top. The <guilabel>Rename Format</guilabel> supports several special "
"parameters, which will be replaced by metadata such as the date the image "
"was created or its filename. They are listed below the text box. You may "
"either click on the parameter name to enter it into the text box or type one "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; importija võib muuta sinu failide nime vastavalt konkreetsele "
"mustrile. Selle seadistamiseks vali all vasakul <guibutton>Seadistused</"
"guibutton>. Selle võimaluse saab sisse või välja lülitada ülal asuva "
"märkekastiga. <guilabel>Ümbernimetamise vorming</guilabel> toetab mitmeid "
"eriparameetreid, mis asendatakse metaandmetega, näiteks pildi loomise aja "
"või failinimega. Need on loetletud tekstikasti all. Võid klõpsata parameetri "
"nimele, et lisada see tekstikasti, või kirjutada selle ise käsitsi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tips"
msgstr "Vihjed"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the mouse"
msgstr "Hiire kasutamine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid "Panning with the mouse"
msgstr "Hiirega kerimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Holding down the left mouse button on an image allows you to scroll the "
"image."
msgstr "Hiire vasakut nuppu pildi kohal all hoides saab pilti kerida."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:522
#, no-c-format
msgid "The mouse wheel will scroll the image up and down."
msgstr "Hiirerattaga saab pilti üles ja alla kerida."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zooming with the mouse"
msgstr "Hiirega suurendamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the middle mouse button will toggle the <guibutton>Fit</guibutton> "
"zoom button. Hold down the &Shift; key and middle-click to toggle the "
"<guibutton>Fill</guibutton> zoom button."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hold down the &Ctrl; key, then either use the mouse wheel to zoom in and out "
"or left click to zoom in and right click to zoom out."
msgstr ""
"Klahvi &Ctrl; all hoides saab kas hiirerattaga suurendada ja vähendada või "
"siis hiire vasaku nupuga klõpsates suurendada ja parema nupuga klõpsates "
"vähendada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:535
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The mouse wheel, used while holding down the &Alt; key, will scroll the "
"image horizontally."
msgstr ""
"Klahvi &Alt; allhoidmisel saab hiirerattaga pilti ka rõhtsuunas kerida."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browsing with the mouse"
msgstr "Hiirega sirvimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:543
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When in Browse mode, clicking an image switches into View mode and shows "
"that image."
msgstr "Sirvimisrežiimis lülitab klõps pildil näitamisrežiimi ja näitab pilti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When in Browse mode, scrolling the mouse wheel will scroll up or down the "
"thumbnail view area."
msgstr ""
"Sirvimisrežiimis kerib hiirerattaga kerimine pisipiltide ala üles või alla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Mouse wheel behavior</guilabel> option in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &gwenview;</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> is set to Browse, scrolling the mouse wheel while "
"in View Mode will move you through the images in the folder."
msgstr ""
"Kui dialoogis <menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>&gwenview; seadistamine</guimenuitem></menuchoice> on "
"<guilabel>hiire käitumiseks</guilabel> valitud sirvimine, võimaldab "
"näitamisrežiimis hiirerattaga kerimine liikuda läbi kataloogi piltide."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid "Key bindings"
msgstr "Kiirklahvid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:558
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&gwenview; comes with a range of keyboard shortcuts, all of which can be "
